eme Leader confirms hardline commanders have seized control & sidelined the elected government. Iran is now an open military junta. Ironically, this might", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 177}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsiVUTyu", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 90, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8652074, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1780307097564, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "JonathanE", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsiVUTyu.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/OjEOZDiZZMoq.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/OjRGUJc5GYtCThNO.jpeg", "width": 733, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UiGbn|j]t8R%~VV@oekDxtjtaeazIVaxWCae", "full_resolution": [1040, 992]}, "title": "Checking in ...", "last_comment_created": 1780309590387, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 1, "score_up": 90, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsiVVZye", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 44, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8652444, "raw_content": "https://x.com/mattforney/status/2061254017628483668?s=20  \r\n  \r\nArticle on how the Trump administration has systematically cut immigrants off from jobs and gibs to force them to leave the country. Everyone---every single person---claiming Trump failed on immigration or is flooding America with Indians or has halted deportations is a complete liar who should be shunned.\r\n\r\nHighlights:\r\n\r\n- First anecdote is about a Salvadoran woman who came here on TPS 30 YEARS AGO. We're supposed to feel bad for her because she got fired from her janitorial job at an airport after the government tightened security clearance requirements. Bukele made la patria safe, tia. Go home.\r\n\r\n- Self-deportations are working. As it turns out, when you want to catch a lot of fish, you drain the pool. Jobs and gibs are the pool that immigrants swim in.\r\n\r\n- The Trump administration is banning the parents of anchor babies from getting day care subsidies, has already banned noncitizens from getting SBA loans, and have banned immigrants from getting CDLs.\r\n\r\n- USCIS is banning asylum seekers from obtaining work permits.\r\n\r\n- Trump has signed an executive order deputizing banks to cut illegals off from banking services and initiated an investigation to uncover immigrants who obtained credit cards fraudulently.\r\n\r\n- Trump banned illegal aliens from receiving free healthcare. Emergency rooms across the country have emptied out because Consuela and Ramesh are no longer clogging them up every time they get the sniffles.\r\n\r\n- Trump has banned immigrants from Head Start and is de facto banning them from receiving child care subsidies.\r\n\r\n- Trump has banned the illegal alien parents of anchor babies from receiving federal child tax credits. The article discusses an illegal couple that saw their tax refund slashed from $3,500 to $300 as a result.\r\n\r\n- Trump has banned illegal aliens from living in public housing.\r\n\r\nIn barely a year in office, Trump has made life so inhospitable to foreign parasites that they're all leaving on their own. Imagine another four, eight, possibly 12 years of this. Forget going back to the 90s, America would look like it did in the 50s.\r\n\r\nGOT WHAT I VOTED FOR AGAIN!", "author": "mightyclaw", "created": 1780321048238, "profile_picture": "SmcextUuNptS", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "MAGA250", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Maybe we're getting what we voted for", "last_comment_created": 1780323059738, "content": "<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://x.com/mattforney/status/2061254017628483668?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/mattforney/status/2061254017628483668?s=20</a></p>\n<p>Article on how the Trump administration has systematically cut immigrants off from jobs and gibs to force them to leave the country. Everyone---every single person---claiming Trump failed on immigration or is flooding America with Indians or has halted deportations is a complete liar who should be shunned.</p>\n<p>Highlights:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>First anecdote is about a Salvadoran woman who came here on TPS 30 YEARS AGO. We're supposed to feel bad for her because she got fired from her janitorial job at an airport after the government tightened security clearance requirements. Bukele made la patria safe, tia. Go home.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Self-deportations are working. As it turns out, when you want to catch a lot of fish, you drain the pool. Jobs and gibs are the pool that immigrants swim in.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Trump administration is banning the parents of anchor babies from getting day care subsidies, has already banned noncitizens from getting SBA loans, and have banned immigrants from getting CDLs.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>USCIS is banning asylum seekers from obtaining work permits.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Trump has signed an executive order deputizing banks to cut illegals off from banking services and initiated an investigation to uncover immigrants who obtained credit cards fraudulently.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Trump banned illegal aliens from receiving free healthcare. Emergency rooms across the country have emptied out because Consuela and Ramesh are no longer clogging them up every time they get the sniffles.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Trump has banned immigrants from Head Start and is de facto banning them from receiving child care subsidies.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Trump has banned the illegal alien parents of anchor babies from receiving federal child tax credits. The article discusses an illegal couple that saw their tax refund slashed from $3,500 to $300 as a result.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Trump has banned illegal aliens from living in public housing.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In barely a year in office, Trump has made life so inhospitable to foreign parasites that they're all leaving on their own. Imagine another four, eight, possibly 12 years of this. Forget going back to the 90s, America would look like it did in the 50s.</p>\n<p>GOT WHAT I VOTED FOR AGAIN!</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 44, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsiVVqtV", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 38, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8652529, "raw_content": "", "author": "Moebius", "created": 1780323847290, "profile_picture": "0F9hm63l5dUw", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Porkbut", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.breitbart.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsiVVqtV.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "h